Four occupants of a saloon car perished on Sunday morning in a grisly accident after the vehicle collided head-on with a bus. The accident occurred at Moredant on the Nakuru-Nairobi highway. Witnesses said the salon car was travelling from Nakuru to Nairobi when it collided with the bus belonging to Climax bus company. Several passengers in the bus sustained injuries and were rushed to Naivasha hospital for treatment. Click here for the latest political news 